@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Introduction";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - French Courier Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        code {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 2px 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Introduction to French Courier Management System</h1>

        <p>Welcome to the introduction page of the French Courier Management System, your comprehensive solution for managing courier operations with ease and efficiency.</p>

        <h2>Project Objectives</h2>
        <p>The primary objectives of our project are:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To develop a user-friendly web application for courier companies and logistics providers.</li>
            <li>To streamline and optimize delivery operations through advanced features and functionalities.</li>
            <li>To provide real-time tracking and management of deliveries, customers, items, and units.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Significance</h2>
        <p>The French Courier Management System holds significant importance for several reasons:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Demonstrates proficiency in ASP.NET MVC 8.0 and Entity Framework.</li>
            <li>Addresses real-world challenges faced by the logistics industry.</li>
            <li>Contributes to enhancing efficiency, accuracy, and customer satisfaction.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>In conclusion, the French Courier Management System is a testament to our dedication, creativity, and technical acumen. We believe that this project will make a meaningful impact in the field of courier management and logistics.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
